Package: nshunter
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: DNSSEC zone exposure analyzer (CLI)
 nshunter assesses how much of a DNS zone is discoverable through DNSSEC
 side-channels (NSEC/NSEC3 walking), optional zone transfers (AXFR), and
 passive sources (certificate transparency registries, zone metadata).
 Reports are stored locally (Pebble + SQLite).
